⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Emma Wilder
node LMZ · LMZ · ⟦Emma Wilder:LMZ:39bbf2⟧

WHO   — Emma Wilder — the one who listens
WHAT  — The chosen heart: the little girl the future's whole hope runs through, who works the spinners, phases through matter, and finally cries the saving tear.
WHERE — LMZ · The Last Mimzy (2007)  Framework inputs: The Last Mimzy (2007, dir. Robert Shaye, New Line); verified cast & facts  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the film's thesis is that salvation comes through innocence, and Emma is the innocence it comes through.
HOW   — By listening to Mimzy when no one else can, learning its gifts, and giving the one tear that heals a world.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  Everyone else studied the toys. I listened to them. And in the end it wasn't a machine that saved us — it was one tear of mine.

